\f0\b\fs38 \cf2 C. Repair station
\f1\b0\fs32 \
\
A certificated repair station may perform maintenance, preventive maintenance, or alterations on articles for which it is rated and within OpSpecs limitations, and may approve RTS for those articles. Repair stations must stay within ratings and available technical data/equipment. For major alterations, Form 337 is still required; for some major repairs, a repair station may use its work order/method allowed by Part 43 Appendix B instead of Form 337.  \
\
